<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Memory Forensics Triage Report — {{ dump_filename }}</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap');
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
    .mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }
    .fade-in { animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease-in; }
    @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(8px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-900 min-h-screen">

<!-- ========================================================
     HERO / VERDICT BANNER
     ======================================================== -->
<header class="{% if verdict == 'Compromised' %}bg-red-700{% elif verdict == 'Suspicious' %}bg-amber-600{% else %}bg-green-700{% endif %} text-white shadow-lg">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-10 fade-in">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <span class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
            {% if verdict == 'Compromised' %}COMPROMISED{% elif verdict == 'Suspicious' %}SUSPICIOUS{% else %}CLEAN{% endif %}
          </span>
          <span class="text-2xl">
            {% if verdict == 'Compromised' %}&#x26A0;{% elif verdict == 'Suspicious' %}&#x26A0;{% else %}&#x2705;{% endif %}
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg opacity-90 font-light">Memory Forensics Triage Report</p>
        <p class="mono text-sm opacity-75 mt-1">{{ dump_filename }}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-center">
        <div class="bg-white/20 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold">{{ process_count }}</p>
          <p class="text-xs opacity-80 uppercase tracking-wider">Processes</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/20 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold">{{ ioc_matches | length }}</p>
          <p class="text-xs opacity-80 uppercase tracking-wider">IOC Hits</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/20 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold">{{ overall_score }}</p>
          <p class="text-xs opacity-80 uppercase tracking-wider">Risk Score</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/20 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold">{{ "%.1f"|format(duration_s) }}s</p>
          <p class="text-xs opacity-80 uppercase tracking-wider">Analysis Time</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-white/20 flex flex-wrap gap-6 text-sm opacity-80">
      <span><strong>Dump:</strong> {{ dump_path }}</span>
      <span><strong>Analysed:</strong> {{ analysis_timestamp }}</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-8 space-y-10">

<!-- ========================================================
     EXECUTIVE SUMMARY
     ======================================================== -->
<section class="fade-in bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
    <span class="w-1 h-6 {% if verdict == 'Compromised' %}bg-red-500{% elif verdict == 'Suspicious' %}bg-amber-500{% else %}bg-green-500{% endif %} rounded-full inline-block"></span>
    Executive Summary
  </h2>
  <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
    {% set flagged = suspect_processes | selectattr("verdict", "ne", "Clean") | list %}
    {% set compromised_procs = suspect_processes | selectattr("verdict", "eq", "Compromised") | list %}
    {% set ioc_actors = ioc_matches | map(attribute="ioc") | map(attribute="actor") | unique | list %}
    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
      <span class="text-blue-500 mt-0.5">&#x2022;</span>
      <span><strong>{{ process_count }}</strong> processes analysed across the memory dump.</span>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
      <span class="{% if flagged %}text-red-500{% else %}text-green-500{% endif %} mt-0.5">&#x2022;</span>
      <span>
        <strong>{{ flagged | length }}</strong> process{% if flagged | length != 1 %}es{% endif %}
        flagged as suspicious or compromised
        {% if compromised_procs %}
          (including <strong>{{ compromised_procs | length }}</strong> with Compromised verdict)
        {% endif %}.
      </span>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
      <span class="{% if ioc_matches %}text-red-500{% else %}text-green-500{% endif %} mt-0.5">&#x2022;</span>
      <span>
        <strong>{{ ioc_matches | length }}</strong> IOC match{% if ioc_matches | length != 1 %}es{% endif %} found
        {% if ioc_actors %}
          across {{ ioc_actors | length }} threat actor{% if ioc_actors | length != 1 %}s{% endif %}:
          <strong>{{ ioc_actors | join(", ") }}</strong>
        {% endif %}.
      </span>
    </li>
    {% set errored = plugin_errors.items() | list %}
    {% if errored %}
    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
      <span class="text-yellow-500 mt-0.5">&#x2022;</span>
      <span><strong>{{ errored | length }}</strong> plugin{% if errored | length != 1 %}s{% endif %} encountered errors during analysis (see Plugin Status section).</span>
    </li>
    {% endif %}
  </ul>
</section>

<!-- ========================================================
     SUSPECT PROCESSES TABLE
     ======================================================== -->
<section class="fade-in">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
    <span class="w-1 h-6 bg-red-500 rounded-full inline-block"></span>
    Suspect Process Risk Analysis
  </h2>
  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="min-w-full text-sm">
        <thead class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 uppercase text-xs tracking-wider">
          <tr>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">PID</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Process</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">PPID</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Image Path</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Score</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Verdict</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Risk Factors</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
          {% for proc in suspect_processes %}
          <tr class="{% if proc.verdict == 'Compromised' %}bg-red-50 hover:bg-red-100{% elif proc.verdict == 'Suspicious' %}bg-amber-50 hover:bg-amber-100{% else %}hover:bg-gray-50{% endif %} transition-colors">
            <td class="px-4 py-3 mono text-gray-600">{{ proc.pid }}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium mono">{{ proc.name }}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 mono text-gray-500">{{ proc.ppid }}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 mono text-xs text-gray-500 max-w-xs truncate" title="{{ proc.path }}">
              {{ proc.path or "—" }}
            </td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full font-bold text-sm
                {% if proc.risk_score >= 70 %}bg-red-100 text-red-700{% elif proc.risk_score >= 30 %}bg-amber-100 text-amber-700{% else %}bg-green-100 text-green-700{% endif %}">
                {{ proc.risk_score }}
              </span>
            </td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold
                {% if proc.verdict == 'Compromised' %}bg-red-100 text-red-700{% elif proc.verdict == 'Suspicious' %}bg-amber-100 text-amber-700{% else %}bg-green-100 text-green-700{% endif %}">
                {{ proc.verdict }}
              </span>
            </td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
                {% for factor in proc.risk_factors %}
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-gray-100 border border-gray-200 rounded text-xs text-gray-700 mono">{{ factor }}</span>
                {% endfor %}
                {% if not proc.risk_factors %}
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-xs">None</span>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          {% else %}
          <tr><td colspan="7" class="px-4 py-8 text-center text-gray-400">No processes to display.</td></tr>
          {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========================================================
     NETWORK CONNECTIONS
     ======================================================== -->
{% set net_rows = network_connections %}
<section class="fade-in">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
    <span class="w-1 h-6 bg-blue-500 rounded-full inline-block"></span>
    Network Connections
    <span class="ml-2 px-2 py-0.5 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-xs rounded-full">{{ net_rows | length }}</span>
  </h2>
  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="min-w-full text-sm">
        <thead class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 uppercase text-xs tracking-wider">
          <tr>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">PID</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Process</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Protocol</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Local Address</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Foreign Address</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">State</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">IOC Flag</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
          {% set net_ioc_ips = ioc_matches | selectattr("ioc.type", "eq", "network_ip") | map(attribute="ioc.value") | list %}
          {% for row in net_rows %}
          {% set foreign = row.get("ForeignAddr") or row.get("ForeignAddress") or "" %}
          {% set is_flagged = foreign.split(":")[0] in net_ioc_ips %}
          <tr class="{% if is_flagged %}bg-red-50{% else %}hover:bg-gray-50{% endif %} transition-colors">
            <td class="px-4 py-3 mono text-gray-600">{{ row.get("PID") or row.get("Pid") or "—" }}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 mono font-medium">{{ row.get("Owner") or row.get("Process") or row.get("Name") or "—" }}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">{{ row.get("Proto") or row.get("Protocol") or "—" }}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 mono text-xs">{{ row.get("LocalAddr") or row.get("LocalAddress") or "—" }}:{{ row.get("LocalPort") or "" }}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 mono text-xs {% if is_flagged %}text-red-700 font-semibold{% endif %}">{{ foreign }}:{{ row.get("ForeignPort") or "" }}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-gray-100 rounded text-xs">{{ row.get("State") or "—" }}</span>
            </td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">
              {% if is_flagged %}
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-red-100 text-red-700 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">IOC MATCH</span>
              {% else %}
              <span class="text-gray-300 text-xs">—</span>
              {% endif %}
            </td>
          </tr>
          {% else %}
          <tr><td colspan="7" class="px-4 py-8 text-center text-gray-400">No network connections found in dump.</td></tr>
          {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========================================================
     IOC MATCHES
     ======================================================== -->
<section class="fade-in">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
    <span class="w-1 h-6 bg-red-500 rounded-full inline-block"></span>
    IOC Matches
    <span class="ml-2 px-2 py-0.5 bg-red-100 text-red-700 text-xs rounded-full">{{ ioc_matches | length }}</span>
  </h2>
  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="min-w-full text-sm">
        <thead class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 uppercase text-xs tracking-wider">
          <tr>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Indicator Value</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Type</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Threat Actor</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Severity</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Matched In</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Process</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Citation</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
          {% for match in ioc_matches %}
          <tr class="hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors">
            <td class="px-4 py-3 mono text-xs font-medium text-gray-800 max-w-xs truncate" title="{{ match.ioc.value }}">
              {{ match.ioc.value }}
            </td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 rounded text-xs mono">{{ match.ioc.type }}</span>
            </td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-gray-700">{{ match.ioc.actor }}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded border text-xs font-semibold {{ match.ioc.severity | severity_color }}">
                {{ match.ioc.severity | upper }}
              </span>
            </td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 mono text-xs text-blue-700">{{ match.plugin }}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 mono text-xs">
              {% if match.process_name %}{{ match.process_name }}{% endif %}
              {% if match.process_pid %} (PID {{ match.process_pid }}){% endif %}
            </td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-xs">
              {% if match.ioc.citation %}
              <a href="{{ match.ioc.citation }}" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline truncate block max-w-xs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                Source &#x2197;
              </a>
              {% else %}—{% endif %}
            </td>
          </tr>
          {% else %}
          <tr><td colspan="7" class="px-4 py-8 text-center text-gray-400">No IOC matches found — memory appears clean of known threat actor indicators.</td></tr>
          {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========================================================
     KERNEL MODULES (modscan)
     ======================================================== -->
<section class="fade-in">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
    <span class="w-1 h-6 bg-purple-500 rounded-full inline-block"></span>
    Loaded Kernel Modules
    <span class="ml-2 px-2 py-0.5 bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 text-xs rounded-full">{{ kernel_modules | length }}</span>
  </h2>
  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="min-w-full text-sm">
        <thead class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 uppercase text-xs tracking-wider">
          <tr>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Offset</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Base</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Size</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Name</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Path</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
          {% for mod in kernel_modules[:50] %}
          <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
            <td class="px-4 py-3 mono text-xs text-gray-500">{{ mod.get("Offset") or "—" }}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 mono text-xs text-gray-500">{{ mod.get("Base") or mod.get("DllBase") or "—" }}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 mono text-xs">{{ mod.get("Size") or "—" }}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 mono font-medium text-sm">{{ mod.get("Name") or mod.get("BaseDllName") or "—" }}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 mono text-xs text-gray-500 max-w-md truncate" title="{{ mod.get('File') or mod.get('FullDllName') or mod.get('Path') or '' }}">
              {{ mod.get("File") or mod.get("FullDllName") or mod.get("Path") or "—" }}
            </td>
          </tr>
          {% else %}
          <tr><td colspan="5" class="px-4 py-8 text-center text-gray-400">No kernel modules found.</td></tr>
          {% endfor %}
          {% if kernel_modules | length > 50 %}
          <tr><td colspan="5" class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-gray-400 text-xs">… and {{ (kernel_modules | length) - 50 }} more modules (truncated for readability)</td></tr>
          {% endif %}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========================================================
     PLUGIN STATUS
     ======================================================== -->
<section class="fade-in">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
    <span class="w-1 h-6 bg-gray-400 rounded-full inline-block"></span>
    Plugin Execution Status
  </h2>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3">
    {% for plugin_name, result in plugin_results.items() %}
    {% set has_error = result.error %}
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border {% if has_error %}border-red-200 bg-red-50{% else %}border-green-200{% endif %} p-4 shadow-sm">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
        <span class="mono font-semibold text-sm">{{ plugin_name }}</span>
        {% if has_error %}
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500 inline-block"></span>
        {% else %}
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 inline-block"></span>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      {% if has_error %}
      <p class="text-xs text-red-600 mt-1 truncate" title="{{ result.error }}">{{ result.error }}</p>
      {% else %}
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">{{ result.rows | length }} rows &middot; {{ "%.2f"|format(result.duration_s) }}s</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========================================================
     NEXT STEPS / IR RECOMMENDATIONS
     ======================================================== -->
<section class="fade-in bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
    <span class="w-1 h-6 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full inline-block"></span>
    Next Steps for the IR Analyst
  </h2>
  <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
    {% if verdict == 'Compromised' %}
    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-700 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</span>
      <span><strong>Isolate the host immediately.</strong> Evidence suggests active compromise. Remove the host from the network while preserving the memory image.</span>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-700 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">2</span>
      <span><strong>Dump and carve suspicious processes.</strong> For each Compromised process above, use <span class="mono bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">vol3 -f dump.raw windows.dumpfiles --pid &lt;PID&gt;</span> to extract the binary for static + dynamic analysis.</span>
    </li>
    {% endif %}
    {% if ioc_matches %}
    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-orange-100 text-orange-700 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">{{ '3' if verdict == 'Compromised' else '1' }}</span>
      <span><strong>Pivot on IOC actors found:</strong> {{ ioc_matches | map(attribute="ioc.actor") | unique | join(", ") }}. Retrieve the latest Threat Intelligence reports for these groups and check for additional TTPs in MITRE ATT&amp;CK.</span>
    </li>
    {% endif %}
    {% set net_rows = network_connections %}
    {% if net_rows %}
    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#x2022;</span>
      <span><strong>Block and investigate C2 IPs.</strong> Add all flagged foreign addresses to firewall blocklists. Query DNS logs, proxy logs, and SIEM for historical connections to these IPs.</span>
    </li>
    {% endif %}
    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#x2022;</span>
      <span><strong>Review registry persistence.</strong> Run <span class="mono bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">vol3 windows.registry.printkey</span> on <span class="mono bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run</span> and <span class="mono bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Image File Execution Options</span>.</span>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#x2022;</span>
      <span><strong>Check lateral movement artifacts.</strong> Examine event logs for 4624/4625 (logon), 4648 (explicit credential use), and 7045 (new service installed).</span>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#x2022;</span>
      <span><strong>Preserve evidence chain.</strong> Hash the original memory dump (SHA-256) and store it in an evidence bag before performing any destructive analysis.</span>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&#x2022;</span>
      <span><strong>Run this tool against disk image.</strong> Cross-correlate memory artifacts with filesystem timeline analysis using <span class="mono bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">fls / mactime</span> from The Sleuth Kit.</span>
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>

</main>

<!-- Footer -->
<footer class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-6 border-t border-gray-200 mt-8 text-sm text-gray-400 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-2">
  <span>Generated by <strong class="text-gray-600">memory-forensics-triage v1.0.0</strong> — Volatility 3 wrapper</span>
  <span class="mono">{{ analysis_timestamp }}</span>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
